<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head> <meta charset="utf-8"/> <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"> <title>Press Releases | Entry Software Corporation</title> <meta name="description" content="Press releases for TeamHeadquarters and Entry Software Corporation."/> <meta name="robots" content="index, follow"/> <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/> <link href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"> <link rel="canonical" href="http://www.entry.com/press-releases.php"/><!--[if lt IE 9]> <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script> <script src="js/respond.min.js"></script><![endif]--> <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/favicon.ico"/> <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/bootstrap/img/apple-touch-icon.png"/> <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="72x72" href="/bootstrap/img/apple-touch-icon-72x72.png"/> <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114" href="/bootstrap/img/apple-touch-icon-114x114.png"/></head><body> <?php include '../public_html/includes/google.html';?> <?php include '../public_html/includes/navbar.php';?> <div class="container"> <div class="jumbotron"> <h1>Press Releases</h1> </div><div class="row"> <div class="col-md-8"> <div class="media panel"> <h2>Entry Software and Ivey Business School to Host June 18th Webinar to Help a Broad Range of Businesses Improve Their IT Organization</h2> <p class="lead">06 June 2014</p><img src="/img/pr-june-6-2014.png" width="225" height="267" alt="press release June 6, 2014" class="media thumbnail pull-left"/> <p>Entry Software Corporation is joining with the esteemed Ivey Business School at Western University and its Associate Professor of Management Information Systems, Dr. Nicole Haggerty, PhD, to present a June 18th Webinar, IT-Enabled IT Organizations - Making Sense of IT Frameworks and Using Technology to Improve Your IT Organization.</p><a href="/media/pr-june-6-2014.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">View press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>Entry Software Team to Attend Gartner IT Summit, June 9-11, 2014 in the Orlando, Florida Area, as a Silver Sponsor of the Event</h2> <p class="lead">03 June 2014</p><img src="/img/gartner-press-release.png" width="225" height="267" alt="press release June 3, 2014" class="media thumbnail pull-left"/> <p>Entry Software Corporation is serving as a Silver Sponsor of the Gartner IT Infrastructure & Operations Management Summit, June 9-11, 2014, in the Orlando, Fla. area. During the event, the Entry team will be showing SMEs the many capabilities of the company's TeamHeadquarters v. 7.0, a fully integrated IT service and project management solution. </p><a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/06/prweb11905486.htm" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">View press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>Entry Software Chosen to be One of Eight Companies on the Ontario Trade Mission to FOSE and Washington, DC</h2> <p class="lead">14 May 2014</p><img src="/img/fose-press-release.png" width="225" height="267" alt="press release May 14, 2014" class="media thumbnail pull-left"/> <p>The government of Ontario Canada has chosen Entry Software Corporation of London Ontario to join the Ontario Trade Mission to FOSE and Washington, DC. This special opportunity was available to only eight Ontario companies. </p><a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/05/prweb11853629.htm" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Download press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>"Reporting Project Status" is #1 Reason IT Projects Are Not Completed on Time, According to Entry Software Research</h2> <p class="lead">28 March 2014</p><img src="/img/pr-28-mar-2014.jpg" width="225" height="261" alt="press release March 28, 2014" class="media thumbnail pull-left"/> <p>According to data from IMTS's 2014 research, as commissioned by Entry Software Corporation, 55 percent of IT managers and corporate executives said that "reporting project status" was the #1 productivity drain on their IT resources, which resulted in IT projects requiring more time than originally estimated.</p><a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/05/prweb11853629.htm" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Download press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>Entry Software's Newest E-Book Enhances IT Project Manager's Understanding of the Importance of Tracking Project Status</h2> <p class="lead">28 February 2014</p><img src="http://www.entry.com/img/pr-28-feb-2014.jpg" class="media thumbnail pull-left" alt="press release February 28, 2014" width="260" height="292"/> <p>Tracking Project Status Throughout the Engagement, the newest e-book from Entry Software and written by Brad Egeland, explains why tracking project status is the most important responsibility of the IT project manager. The book will also improve their management of project risks, scheduling, scope and resources required for a successful completion.</p><a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/03/prweb11626256.htm" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Download press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>Entry Software Research Identifies Unacceptable Project Delays Among 37 Percent of IT Managers and Corporate Executives</h2> <p class="lead">26 February 2014</p><img src="http://www.entry.com/img/pr-26-feb-2014.jpg" class="media thumbnail pull-left" alt="press release February 26, 2014" width="260" height="292"/> <p>During early 2014, Entry Software commissioned an independent research firm to conduct extensive live interviews with more than 150 IT managers and corporate executives in the United States and found that 37 percent of them stated their IT projects required significantly more time to complete than initially scheduled.</p><a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/02/prweb11617550.htm" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Download press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>Entry Software's TeamHeadquarters, V.7, Integrates <abbr title="Information Technology Service Management">ITSM</abbr> and Project Management to Maximize Business Value from IT</h2> <p class="lead">29 November 2013</p><img src="http://www.entry.com/img/pr-29-november-2013.jpg" class="media thumbnail pull-left" alt="press release November 29, 2013" width="260" height="292"/> <p>With the forthcoming release of TeamHeadquarters, version 7, Entry Software enhances its position in the IT Service Management marketplace with a comprehensive ITIL best-practices tool that delivers more of what IT actually does for the enterprise and its customers.</p><a href="http://www.entry.com/media/pr-29-november-2013.pdf" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Download press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>TeamHeadquarters Project Management and ITSM All in One Solution - Release Candidate Announced</h2> <p class="lead">27 September 2013</p><img class="media pull-left thumbnail" src="http://www.entry.com/img/pr-27-september-2013.jpg" alt="Press release September 27, 2013" width="260" height="292"/> <p>Entry Software Corporation announced today that its TeamHeadquarters 7.0 software has been made available as a Release Candidate (RC). Customers, interested parties and beta testers can now test and validate the software</p><a href="http://www.entry.com/media/pr-27-september-2013.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Download press release</a> </div><div class="media panel"> <h2>Innovative IT Work Management Software to Revolutionize IT Organizations Everywhere</h2> <p class="lead">17 April 2013</p><img class="media pull-left thumbnail" src="http://www.entry.com/img/pr-17-april-2013.jpg" alt="press release April 17 2013" width="260" height="292"/> <p>Entry Software Corporation of London Ontario Canada announces that TeamHeadquarters V.7.0 Integrated IT Work Management software for Service Desk and Project Management will revolutionize IT Organizations everywhere</p><a href="http://www.entry.com/media/pr-17-april-2013.pdf" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Download press release</a> </div><div class="media"> <h2>Forest Park Medical Center Press Release</h2> <p class="lead">13 September 2012</p><img class="media thumbnail pull-left" src="http://www.entry.com/img/forest-park-medical-center-press-release.jpg" alt="forest park medical center press release" width="260" height="292"/> <p>Entry Software Corporation and Forest Park Medical Centers have signed an agreement to implement TeamHeadquarters help desk and project management software to consolidate existing separate systems, optimize costs and deliver high quality service.</p><p><a href="http://www.entry.com/media/forest-park-medical-center-press-release.pdf" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Download press release</a></p></div></div><div class="col-md-4"> <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked panel well"> <li><a href="/about.html">About Entry Software</a></li><li><a href="/ceo-message.html">Message from the CEO</a></li><li><a href="http://www.entry.com/our-story.html">Our Story</a></li><li class="active"><a href="/press-releases.html">Press Releases</a></li><li><a href="/quotes-case-studies.html">Customer Quote and Case Studies</a></li><li><a href="/events.html">Events</a></li><li><a href="/contact.html">Contact Us</a></li></ul><img class="float-right" src="http://www.entry.com/img/mission.png" alt="mission statement" width="360" height="146"/></div></div></div><div id="footer"> <?php include '../public_html/includes/footer.html';?> </div></body></html>